Type: Package
Package: backgroudjobR
Title: Execute R Code in Background with Error Handling and Logging
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Zhiming", "Ye", , "garnetcrow@hotmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools to execute R scripts in a controlled
    environment with comprehensive error handling, logging, and state
    saving capabilities. Allows running background jobs with external
    variables and saves execution state when errors occur.
